{"tid":2509391,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]GUNDAM BATTLE OPERATION 2 [95] 1001 唔開post 一世抽垃圾","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T03:22:20.000Z","uid":152969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"78dc9e85c0e9f01810cc8a1174a3fe7c7c00afb5","tid":2509391,"uid":152969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYpANaYsV19cwwj5xuv4rRZZMv1LMb9GSdpYPWsPYmqGM?filename=w7gBX9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7gBX9m.jpg&h=114766dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=d5077e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=80943adc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=9623d96f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\nGBO2 機體表<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=879f206f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n新手注意<br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=84189bbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解我成日斷線<br />\nA. 為己為人, 自殺對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?<br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\nQ. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?<br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\nQ. 可唔可以同朋友一齊開房玩<br />\nA. Ranking 同Quick請用正方入房之後邀朋友, 自訂直接入房之後邀朋友<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣用支援炮擊<br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\nQ. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?<br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣放炸彈<br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按正方裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)<br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n(Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\nQ:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？<br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得<br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出反格<br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\nQ. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬<br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?<br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, One_For_All, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈,絕影OuO<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡"},{"pid":"851dde64467f708c432644980af5ba7d31a9516c","tid":2509391,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"擺低一張上星期嘅J圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3jW3M4TG6xeGy5RFd1G6E1oZhAbEov3mJPNjEH6LVhX?filename=gdrFFpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdrFFpE.jpg&h=86129585&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c95f5625b7e6b50d15333ce3e3444223a945295","tid":2509391,"uid":17459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6b052409a8fa1bae9e275c0bf75672ff7d67f2","tid":2509391,"uid":90535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defec912006713cc00454d1d05ad6c5648ef6fa1","tid":2509391,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"新po留名<br />\n1001 唔開新post嗰個做開食屎狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee789757fea7573acafa15a3167341d66e0719b","tid":2509391,"uid":127611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c95f5625b7e6b50d15333ce3e3444223a945295","tid":2509391,"uid":17459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68da04d3000fca1d71423fbf83c5f08c5a4190d6","tid":2509391,"uid":244282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"我係黎食花生留個名既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7